latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Dancing with my favorite dance partner @_step.it.up 💜
Working out has never been more fun! 
But all I can think after this, is eating “yummy jalebis”. 🙈

 Disclaimer : We’re not certified Zumba instructors. Just enthusiasts who started doing Zumba together and have loved it ever since!
This right here was an absolute fun package! 💯

Editing & effects by @hargungandhii , who’s absolutely brilliant at what he does & has worked very patiently with us demanding maniacs, haha. 

Choreographed by :- @dontcallmekanye & @_step.it.up 

Song : Yummy Jalebi by @tesherrrr
